## Implementation Plan: Unified StripeCheckout Component

### Overview

The plan creates a single shared `StripeCheckout` component at `components/StripeCheckout.tsx` and integrates it into 3 page files: `Recharge.tsx`, `Plan.tsx`, and `Account.tsx`. The component provides a consistent Stripe-branded payment UI with fake card inputs today, structured for a straightforward swap to real `@stripe/react-stripe-js` Elements in the future.

The reference codebase is **SaaS X-Final-Rick-Test** (`C:\Users\User\Downloads\SaaS X-Final-Rick-Test`), a Vite + React SPA with Tailwind dark theme, Lucide icons, and page-level routing managed in `App.tsx`.

---

